title: 105_s2399
content: TEMPORARY DUTY SUSPENSIONS ON CERTAIN HIV DRUG SUBSTANCES are being amended in the Harmonized Tariff Schedule of the United States. New headings are being inserted in numerical sequence. "9902.32.14 (S)-N-tert-butyl-1,2,3,4-tetrahydro-3-isoquinoline carboxamide (CAS No. 149182-72-9) provided for in" (S)-N-tert-butyl-1,2,3,4-tetrahydro-3-isoquinoline carboxamide (CAS No. 149182-72-9) with tariff code 2933.40.60 has no changes and must be imported before 6/30/99. (S)-N-tert-butyl-1,2,3,4-tetrahydro-3-isoquinoline carboxamide hydrochloride salt (CAS No. 149057-17-0) with tariff code 2933.40.60 has no changes and must be imported before 6/30/99. (S)-N-tert-butyl-1,2,3,4-tetrahydro-3-isoquinoline carboxamide sulfate salt (CAS No. 186537-30-4) is provided for. (S)-N-tert-butyl-1,2,3,4-tetrahydro-3-isoquinoline carboxamide sulfate salt (CAS No. 186537-30-4) is provided for. 2933.40.60 - No change. 9902.32.20 - (3S)-1,2,3,4-tetrahydroisoquinoline-3-carboxylic acid (CAS No. 74163-XXXXX) on or before 6/30/99. (S)-N-tert-butyl-1,2,3,4-tetrahydro-3-isoquinoline carboxamide sulfate salt (CAS No. 186537-30-4) is provided for in subheading 2933.40.60. No changes. On or before 6/30/99. The amendment made by subsection (a) applies to goods entered or withdrawn from warehouse for consumption 15 days after the enactment of this Act.
